					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Yeah, I try and make my articles just skirt that edge. Not 100% serious with a little bit of humor or goofiness, but still believable for the Foundation.</p> <p>Instead of lolfoundation, it's yeahfoundation or something. Less &quot;utter lack of restraint and using dangerous anomalies for laughs&quot;, more &quot;workplace shenanigans while still doing the job&quot;</p> 
				 	]]>
